702295f-a.title: Brooklyn: 3rd Avenue - 37th Street
702295f-a.text:
3rd Avenue, north from 37th Street, showing the Bush Terminal
buildings. On the east side of the avenue can be seen construction
work on the Gowanus Parkway.
View 2 shows 37th Street houses.
P. L. Bperr  January, 1941
NO REPRODTCTIONS  Views 1,2
